Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.62,0:00:39.43,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}不管是誰 對未來都著著一股不安的期望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.67,0:00:47.94,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}就朝著明天大步邁進吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.94,0:00:51.07,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}GUNPARADE MARCH
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.11,0:00:57.71,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}總有一天會覺醒的 真實心扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.89,0:01:03.85,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}現在就伸出雙手去感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.06,0:01:13.90,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}在這開始變化的世界 立刻前往探尋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.17,0:01:19.84,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}牽繫著你的手絕不再分離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.78,0:01:22.94,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}因為有你在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.08,0:01:27.52,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}所以一定找尋的到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.16,0:01:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會因為這種事而驚訝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.03,0:01:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然也不會高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.03,0:01:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正裏頭一定是空的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.07,0:01:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是傳說中的鈔票嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.28,0:02:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失主給我兩千元當作謝禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.62,0:02:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會發生什麼好事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.36,0:02:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是某種巨大災難的前兆呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.91,0:02:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.35,0:02:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,振作一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.68,0:02:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「第十話  悲傷你好」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.59,0:02:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,導演是班長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.69,0:02:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大道具是若宮、照明是森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.60,0:02:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,音響則是瀧川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.70,0:02:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來是角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.27,0:03:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男生抽藍色 女生抽紅色的簽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.12,0:03:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抽到一號的是誰呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.89,0:03:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.19,0:03:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,國王是瀨戶口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.22,0:03:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想當國王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.76,0:03:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不要一下子就死的角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.70,0:03:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是角色是公平抽籤的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.03,0:03:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,適合我的角色只有勇敢的騎士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.17,0:03:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愛上公主的紳士英雄非我莫屬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.91,0:03:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算你這麼說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.98,0:03:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瀨戶口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.25,0:03:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓芳野老師困擾的學生 我絕對不會原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.19,0:03:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼二號是誰呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.66,0:03:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來須是壞魔法師對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.23,0:04:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是抽到二號嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.77,0:04:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那為什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.24,0:04:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,台詞太多了 我想當後台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.97,0:04:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是來須…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.31,0:04:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓芳野老師哭泣的學生 就由我來對付吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.92,0:04:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得有點累了 善行 交給你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.37,0:04:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再來六號是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.94,0:04:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是望望美 望望美抽到六號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.14,0:04:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,望望美當妖精啊 這很合適呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.65,0:04:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來就不用問了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.02,0:04:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,七號公主是芝村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.95,0:04:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,八號侍女一定是田邊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.76,0:04:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,七號是芝村是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.96,0:04:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.53,0:05:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是八號的侍女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.60,0:05:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加藤 出這種錯真不像你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.84,0:05:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼忘記把公主的簽放進去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.61,0:05:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 我好像不小心做兩個侍女的簽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.91,0:05:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這麼一回事吧 田邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.35,0:05:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,田邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.29,0:05:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,田邊 你怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.00,0:05:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我今天起也要戴眼鏡了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.37,0:05:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有視力我很有自信的說\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(七號 公主)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.51,0:05:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我總覺得忐忑不安呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.81,0:05:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,田邊該不會發生什麼大事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.38,0:05:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次我們部隊要擔任PBE任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.52,0:06:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啟動助理會是田邊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.96,0:06:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畢竟她已經實習結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.03,0:06:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.39,0:06:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,學姊只是杞人憂天吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.80,0:06:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,田邊現在會這樣 只是以前的反作用力罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.33,0:06:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要小看田邊真紀這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.90,0:06:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她的不幸可不是普通的不幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.84,0:06:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,田邊得到擔任公主 演女主角這種小小幸福的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.85,0:06:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定會遭遇恐怖的災難呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.82,0:06:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽你這麼認真在說 還真恐怖…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.92,0:06:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我打算用這台來拍田邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.76,0:06:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拍錄影帶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.93,0:06:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.06,0:06:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最壞的狀況 田邊可能會掛掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.06,0:06:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時把這卷「最後的英姿」寄給她家人 不是很好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.37,0:06:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小祭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.57,0:06:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界上有些玩笑是不能開的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.38,0:06:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大姊 怎麼用我的腔調講話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.58,0:07:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明你這麼不幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.45,0:07:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼不幸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.59,0:07:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小舞 這個字要怎麼念？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.22,0:07:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為毀滅的我嘆息而流淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.02,0:07:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明你這麼不幸 竟然還為毀滅的我嘆息而流淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.73,0:07:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.96,0:07:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,溫柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.60,0:07:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,溫柔的女孩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.24,0:07:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於公主的美遠近馳名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.18,0:07:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了見公主一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.61,0:07:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大廳聚集了王宮貴族及騎士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.62,0:07:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎各位今天來到這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.42,0:07:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,公主如今亭亭玉立 如今只需要找個好女婿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.99,0:07:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若宮呢 他不是負責大道具嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.70,0:07:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不是還擔任旁白嗎 要等念完台詞才會來做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.77,0:07:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他身體撐得住啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.27,0:07:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用擔心那個笨蛋壯牛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.07,0:08:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何況需要擔心的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.78,0:08:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,需要擔心的是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.15,0:08:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是來須
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.01,0:08:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是慶祝之宴 你為何而來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.59,0:08:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來是為了告訴各位一則預言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.46,0:08:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是為了來宣告死亡 奪走一切的希望而來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.23,0:08:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽清楚了 悲哀土地的後裔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.16,0:08:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,汝等的土地將世代受到諂咒 水將會變得腐爛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.58,0:08:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來須他只要講太多話 好像就會不舒服的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.65,0:08:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像我這樣的帥哥 為什麼要戴鬍子當老頭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.96,0:08:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次真是不順啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.83,0:08:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是當傭人而已啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.20,0:08:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別這麼說 你很高興吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.70,0:08:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪有這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.33,0:09:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小志、小隆、小陽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.30,0:09:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們看你們看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.54,0:09:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.48,0:09:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很適合你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.71,0:09:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小舞的衣服也作好囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.35,0:09:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟小志是一組的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.32,0:09:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要綵排了 我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.26,0:09:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,設定中僕人跟侍女是夫婦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.39,0:09:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速水 你其實很高興對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.00,0:09:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老實一點嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.77,0:09:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,親愛的 振作一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.37,0:09:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如今國王跟皇后已經過世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.91,0:09:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如今公主已經浪跡天涯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.88,0:09:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這寬廣嚴苛的世界裏 公主能夠依靠的只有我們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.75,0:09:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算你這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.12,0:09:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是就算你這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.76,0:10:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對方是恐怖的魔法師 我們根本不是他的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.10,0:10:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然還是選錯角色了吧\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(你也看到了吧)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.10,0:10:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,侍女看起來比較有氣質呢\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(軍隊一瞬間就化為灰燼)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.87,0:10:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過我覺得啊\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(我當然看到啦)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.14,0:10:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,田邊當起公主也不錯呢\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(我們只擅長做飯跟鋪床)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.54,0:10:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本沒辦法揮劍作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.78,0:10:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說的其實也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.28,0:10:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被懦弱附身的僕人夫婦拋棄公主而自己逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.06,0:10:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣 黑夜過去 清晨來臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.83,0:10:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不吉的雲覆蓋著大地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.07,0:10:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是惡靈作祟嗎 還是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.97,0:10:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是位美麗的女性啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.47,0:10:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一看就知道身份相當高貴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.94,0:10:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,PBE活性化成功！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.45,0:11:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 我搞錯了 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.82,0:11:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,休息一下吃個飯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.33,0:11:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然還是選錯角色了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.61,0:11:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟遠阪對戲時 你好像很不自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.12,0:11:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我自己也知道 雖然知道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.99,0:11:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是無論如何身體都會僵硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.63,0:11:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…難道對…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.00,0:11:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,換句話說 你對遠阪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.97,0:11:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請不要笑我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.84,0:11:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會笑你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.14,0:11:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要對大家保守秘密喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.74,0:11:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會說出來的 只會藏在心裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.98,0:11:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村願意聽我說嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.28,0:12:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是在去年的四月 櫻花開始綻放的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.25,0:12:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 就是一年最美的季節 春天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.13,0:12:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有十元銅板而困擾的我 面前出現上天派來的使者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.04,0:12:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.80,0:12:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亮麗的黑髮、清澈的墨綠眼睛 溫柔且溫暖的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.38,0:12:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓人想起古代希臘的雕刻 那位面容尊貴的青年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.18,0:12:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣從我的面前離開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.69,0:12:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個古代希臘什麼的是遠阪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.69,0:12:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.89,0:12:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那之後呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.19,0:12:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我打了一通電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.56,0:12:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是尚敬高中嗎 請幫我轉接5121部隊整備小組
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.20,0:12:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起對不起對不起 我是田邊 真是對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.84,0:13:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕 那是汽油車啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.85,0:13:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後的兩個月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.18,0:13:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我心中都是那個人的身影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.06,0:13:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而在上學的第一天 我知道他是同個部隊的學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.73,0:13:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好高興 真的好感謝神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.73,0:13:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次你們是男女主角 加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.70,0:13:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多加練習 一定就會變得自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.24,0:13:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.71,0:13:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村 我可以問一個問題嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.61,0:13:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.61,0:13:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村對速水沒什麼感覺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.62,0:13:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼是指？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.15,0:13:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,換句話說就是喜歡之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.59,0:13:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼要這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.12,0:13:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確如此吧 我是這麼確信的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.09,0:13:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確信？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.90,0:13:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 我還是說出來好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.26,0:14:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速水不是都有點懦弱嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.17,0:14:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.27,0:14:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得那種的不適合芝村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.78,0:14:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.78,0:14:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.48,0:14:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,適合芝村的必須像男子漢 而且還要有包容力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.68,0:14:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像速水那樣的人不適合你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.29,0:14:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也不是這麼不值得一提
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.29,0:14:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他其實也有像男人的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.66,0:14:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然可能很難相信 但卻是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.66,0:14:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚至連一開始的我都不相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.17,0:14:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,田邊 我們來練習吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.71,0:14:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時間已經不夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.46,0:15:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位久等了 馬上就會開演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.84,0:15:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緊急廣播、緊急廣播
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.34,0:15:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇土地區出現幻獸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.21,0:15:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5121部隊盡速準備出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.22,0:15:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重複一次 5121部隊盡速準備出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.22,0:15:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要讓我們等多久啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.96,0:15:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不開始嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.12,0:15:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位先聽我說一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.96,0:15:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姊姊你又要說冷笑話了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.73,0:15:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是笑話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.00,0:15:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就想說有可能這樣 所以我已經先編輯好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.27,0:15:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不愧是加藤呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.14,0:15:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(壞魔法師跟最後的王國)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.52,0:15:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是很久以前的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.88,0:15:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一座小小的王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.25,0:16:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,王國的人民都勤樸儉實 過著相當幸福的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.36,0:16:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,魔性之人 這裏是慶祝之宴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.23,0:16:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為何而來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.27,0:16:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來是為了告訴各位一則預言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.27,0:16:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是為了來宣告死亡 奪走一切的希望而來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.61,0:16:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽清楚了 悲哀土地的後裔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.75,0:16:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,汝等的土地將世代受到諂咒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.42,0:16:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,王國跟軍隊都被毀滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.42,0:16:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從魔法師手中逃脫出來的只有公主跟一對僕人夫婦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.40,0:16:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是個詭異的森林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.43,0:16:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真希望盡快穿越啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.07,0:16:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,公主 我們先走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.77,0:16:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如今只能等待枯萎 真是朵可憐的玫瑰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.51,0:17:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有水 應該就會嬌艷欲滴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.82,0:17:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然想把你種在王城的庭園 然而如今我卻沒有半寸土地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.09,0:17:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,公主快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.96,0:17:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請原諒棄你而去的我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.43,0:17:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主腦確認 位置西南方兩公里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.47,0:17:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,護衛幻獸群正往東南方散開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.14,0:17:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突破敵方防禦線之後 就進行PBE搬運作業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.81,0:17:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,公主流下來的眼淚 滲入了枯萎玫瑰的根部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.88,0:17:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,此時神奇的事情發生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.89,0:17:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明你這麼不幸 竟然還為毀滅的我嘆息而流淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.43,0:17:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是個溫柔的女孩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.23,0:17:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣的人是地上的至寶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.52,0:18:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,PBE開始準備啟動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.22,0:18:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重複一次 開始準備啟動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.02,0:18:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始進行啟動準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.87,0:18:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人無法以劍打倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.51,0:18:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您是哪位呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.37,0:18:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是被你拯救生命的人 我是你的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.59,0:18:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,PBE活性化成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.79,0:18:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,汝等不可能打倒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.70,0:18:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我即是恐怖、我即是憎恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.30,0:19:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我一起唱和吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.24,0:19:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.07,0:19:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不憎恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.47,0:19:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不憎恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.04,0:19:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不畏懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.51,0:19:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不畏懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.41,0:19:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不憎恨也不畏懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.91,0:19:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這塊土地的後裔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.92,0:19:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能克服恐怖跟憎恨嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.09,0:19:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的畏懼將會成為憎恨\N我的憎恨將會變成恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.43,0:19:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此我不憎恨也不畏懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.40,0:19:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作戰成功 主腦消滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.94,0:19:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毒氣濃度急速下降中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.74,0:19:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在開始回收 HWT歸隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.11,0:19:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,田邊 辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.88,0:19:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.12,0:19:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真紀、真紀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.15,0:19:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(劇終)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.54,0:20:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不敢相信 田邊太走運了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.44,0:20:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然會有這種事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.91,0:20:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是鹵馬鈴薯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.08,0:20:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,田邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.35,0:20:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的電話 是你母親打來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.09,0:20:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.05,0:20:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.19,0:20:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火災？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.36,0:20:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部都燒光了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.66,0:20:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保險能不能給付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.50,0:20:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.17,0:20:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了 那我掛電話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.01,0:20:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,田邊 心情不要太低落喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.14,0:20:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好幸福 幸福到感覺好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.88,0:20:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,家裏所有人都沒有受傷
